Detailed Description

This is a wrapper class around the different EIG_PQ(GT1) classes. It is decided at compile time from which EIG_* file this class inherits. Compile with PQ to inherit from EIG_PQ, compile with PQG to inherit from EIG_PQG, etc. . This way, you can use the EIG object everywhere in the program without having to worry about which conditions are used.
